### 1. List all provider events — no filters
GET http://localhost:8080/provider-events

> {%
  client.global.set("eventGUID", response.body.data.content[0].guid);
%}

### 2. List provider events — paginated
GET http://localhost:8080/provider-events?page=0&pageSize=5

### 3. Filter by event type
GET http://localhost:8080/provider-events?eventType=ProviderFirmChangedSnapshotEvent

### 4. Filter by correlation ID
GET http://localhost:8080/provider-events?correlationId=my-correlation-id

### 5. Filter by event type and correlation ID
GET http://localhost:8080/provider-events?eventType=ProviderFirmChangedSnapshotEvent&correlationId=my-correlation-id

### 6. Get a single event by GUID (uses GUID captured in step 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/provider-events/{{eventGUID}}

### 7. Get a single event — unknown GUID (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/provider-events/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### 8. Get a single event — invalid GUID format (expect 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/provider-events/not-a-valid-uuid
